'''Ifuɣa''' (asget : Afaɣi) d tawsit (taqbilt) tahewwart (ccarif) n [[Imucaɣ|Yimucaɣ]] n Imrabṭen (Inselmen) s laṣel U-Jana (Ijnaten). 


Kel Ifuɣa llan deg [[Mali]] ([[Aẓawad]]) deg temnaṭ n [[Kidal]] ula deg [[Adrar n Ifuɣa|Wedrar n Ifuɣa]]. Tigti deg-sen llan d imeksawen d iserdasen. 

